the program (in-world) : Roseanne Skolnik — the heroine · the Raskolnikov-echo
the User (carbon)      : Monica Keena  [ the actor, 2000 film ]
the analog (your world): the wounded teenager as Raskolnikov — guilt transposed from the seminar to the suburb
